- 120sqm plus character offices
- Full building opportunity
- Massive exposure, signage potential
- 6 free onsite car parks 

Situated in a thriving vibrant precinct on the cusp of the Brisbane CBD, 21 Musgrave Road is a must see for your business. The building features polished Hoop Pine timber flooring, exceptional natural light throughout, excellent ceiling height and a large staff break out area at no extra cost! 

The tenancy has been previously fitted out with a reception, boardroom, separate office and light filled open plan work areas. The property is located seconds from public transport and walking distance to Kelvin Grove Urban Village, The Barracks and Normanby Hotel.

Offices of this calibre are extremely rare. First to inspect will lease! For further information or to arrange an inspection contact the marketing agents CBRE.

CBRE are excited to bring to the market for lease 25 Musgrave Road, Red Hill.

An enviable address located in a thriving, vibrant precinct presenting a unique opportunity for business to combine both work and lifestyle.

- 2500-3036sqm of modern creative style fitted out office space
- Character building 2km from the CBD
- Fully cabled, ready to move in, plug in and start working
- 60 Onsite Car Parking Bays 
- Walk to Suncorp Stadium & Entertainment Venues 
- Next Door to the Normanby Hotel
- Walk to the Barracks and Kelvin Grove Urban Village 
- Large Café Style, fully equipped kitchens 
- Indoor and out door break out workspaces 
- Direct access to public transport
- Massive exposure and signage opportunities 
- 4.5 Star NABERS Energy Rating 

With exceptional ceiling height, large New York style windows and an abundance of natural light, the property presents itself to a variety of creative, professional and mixed use style users looking to be situated in a prime location on the cusp of the Brisbane CBD. 

Spanning over two levels, the tenancies fit out consists of large open plan light filled workspaces, multiple separate offices, boardroom, meeting rooms and fully cabled workstations with furniture throughout. 

The property has large kitchens on both levels, lockers, bike racks and showers. High level security systems are in place and disabled facilities are catered for on each level. 

25 Musgrave Road, Red Hill is easily accessible to all parts of Brisbane and only 20 minutes from the Airport being situated on 3 major transport corridors, Kelvin Grove Road, Musgrave Road and the Inner City By Pass. Both inbound and outbound bus services are at your door step and Roma Street train station is just a short walk away. Cafes, restaurants and bars are all seconds away offering a plethora of staff amenity.
 
25 Musgrave Road is the perfect ‘Work From Home’ precinct. The property has been priced very competitively to lease. 

For further information or to arrange an inspection contact your Exclusive Marketing Agents CBRE.
